---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - GameLayer">
	<main id="main-content">
		<Header />
		
		<section class="privacy-policy">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="policy-content">
					<h1>GameLayer Privacy Policy</h1>
					<p class="last-updated">Last updated: 01.12.25</p>
					<p class="contact-info">Email: <a href="mailto:legal@gamelayer.co">legal@gamelayer.co</a></p>
					<p class="contact-info">Company: GameLayer Oy (Company ID 2503589-1)</p>
					<p class="contact-info">Country: Finland</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
					<p>GameLayer Oy ("GameLayer", "we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your personal data is handled responsibly.</p>
					<p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect personal data when you:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Visit our website(s)</li>
						<li>Use our software platform, APIs, dashboards, or services</li>
						<li>Register for an account or purchase paid plans</li>
					</ul>
					<p>By using our Services, you accept the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
					<p>We collect personal information to provide, maintain, and improve our Services.</p>
					
					<h3>A. Information You Provide</h3>
					<p>This includes:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Name and contact details (e.g., business email, phone number, job title, company)</li>
						<li>Account registration data</li>
						<li>Payment and billing information (when applicable)</li>
						<li>Communication preferences and support requests</li>
					</ul>
					
					<h3>B. Automatically Collected Data</h3>
					<p>We also collect data automatically when you interact with our websites/services, such as:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>IP address and device/browser information</li>
						<li>Usage and analytics data (pages visited, timestamps, interactions)</li>
						<li>Cookies and similar technologies (with consent)</li>
					</ul>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
					<p>We use personal data for purposes including:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Providing and improving our Services</li>
						<li>Managing your account and communicating with you</li>
						<li>Billing and payment processing</li>
						<li>Marketing and promotional communications (with consent)</li>
						<li>Security, fraud prevention, and legal compliance</li>
					</ul>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
					<p>Where applicable, we rely on legal bases such as:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Contract performance (to provide Services you request)</li>
						<li>Legitimate interests (service improvement, analytics)</li>
						<li>Consent (for cookies, direct marketing)</li>
						<li>Legal compliance (where required by law)</li>
					</ul>
					<p>We process personal data only to the extent necessary for the purposes described in this policy.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>5. Sharing and Disclosure of Personal Information</h2>
					<p>We may share personal data:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>With our data processors (e.g., analytics, hosting, CRM providers) under contractual controls that require them to protect your data</li>
						<li>With law enforcement or authorities when legally required</li>
						<li>With service providers that help us deliver our Services</li>
					</ul>
					<p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
					<p>We may use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Enable core functionality</li>
						<li>Collect analytics (e.g., via Google Analytics)</li>
						<li>Personalise your experience</li>
					</ul>
					<p>We obtain consent where required by law and provide controls for cookie preferences.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
					<p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined here, including legal, accounting, or reporting requirements.</p>
					<p>When data is no longer required, we securely delete or anonymise it.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>8. Data Security</h2>
					<p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect personal data against loss, theft, misuse, unauthorised access, alteration, and destruction.</p>
					<p>In the event of a breach that poses a high risk to your rights and freedoms, we will notify you and the relevant authorities without undue delay.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>9. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
					<p>Depending on your location, you may have rights including:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Access:</strong> Request details of personal data we hold about you</li>
						<li><strong>Correction:</strong> Have inaccurate data corrected</li>
						<li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your personal data</li>
						<li><strong>Object or Restrict:</strong> Object to certain processing (e.g., marketing)</li>
						<li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> Receive your personal data in a structured format</li>
					</ul>
					<p>To exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@gamelayer.co">legal@gamelayer.co</a>. We aim to respond within required legal timeframes.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>10. International Data Transfers</h2>
					<p>Your data may be processed outside your jurisdiction (e.g., in servers or by processors located outside the EU/EEA). When this occurs, we apply appropriate safeguards (e.g., standard contractual clauses) to protect your data.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
					<p>We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices, legal requirements, or Services.</p>
					<p>The updated policy will include a "Last updated" date, and significant changes will be communicated where appropriate.</p>
					
					<hr class="section-divider">
					
					<h2>12. Contact Information</h2>
					<p>For privacy questions, data access requests, or concerns:</p>
					<p>
						GameLayer Oy<br>
						Company ID: 2503589-1<br>
						Finland<br>
						Email: <a href="mailto:legal@gamelayer.co">legal@gamelayer.co</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<Footer />
	</main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
.privacy-policy {
	padding: 80px 0;
	background-color: #fff;
	min-height: calc(100vh - 116px - 120px);
	font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
	
	.policy-content {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
		
		h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
			color: #000;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			text-align: left;
			font-weight: 700;
			line-height: 1.2;
		}
		
		.last-updated {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			color: #666;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			font-weight: 400;
		}
		
		.contact-info {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			color: #666;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			font-weight: 400;
		}
		
		.section-divider {
			border: none;
			border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
		}
		
		h2 {
			font-size: 1.875rem;
			color: #000;
			margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 1.3;
		}
		
		h3 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			color: #000;
			margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem 0;
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 1.3;
		}
		
		p {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
			color: #333;
			margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		}
		
		ul {
			margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
			padding-left: 0;
			
			li {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #333;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
				list-style-type: disc;
			}
		}
		
		strong {
			font-weight: 600;
			color: #000;
		}
		
		a {
			color: #0066cc;
			text-decoration: none;
			
			&:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		}
		
		// Responsive design
		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
			}
			
			h2 {
				font-size: 1.625rem;
			}
			
			h3 {
				font-size: 1.35rem;
			}
			
			p, ul li, .contact-info, .last-updated {
				font-size: 1.35rem;
			}
		}
		
		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			h1 {
				font-size: 2.25rem;
			}
			
			h2 {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			h3 {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
			}
			
			p, ul li, .contact-info, .last-updated {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
			}
			
			.policy-content {
				padding: 0 15px;
			}
		}
	}
}
</style>
